{"tid":1382841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得無力既和理非入一入","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:36:30.000Z","uid":98225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"211cb9ed9c00ccd9ef12d4593cf42cd8604d3d59","tid":1382841,"uid":98225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"希望咁多位和理非可以認真對待罷工<br />\n兩個月來 和平示威 勇武爬山 國際輿論下<br />\n香港政府都可以視之為無物<br />\n已經證明佢唔再係人民既政府<br />\n<br />\n絕對明白香港人好有責任感同自私<br />\n所以今次發起既罷工俾足夠時間大家同公司溝通<br />\n(建議大家可以connect 同事組隊先)<br />\n後果一定有 如果真係秋後算帳我覺得你都要諗下係咪仲留係個到(For example CCTVB)<br />\n<br />\n年輕既一輩已經花光佢地既積蓄、勇氣、前途<br />\n如果你覺得你可以置身事外 我真係恭喜你<br />\n你已經成為你地最討厭既人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfic70z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnfic70z.png&h=24301187&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUkbD7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUkbD7f.png&h=79b2fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYtkxsf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYtkxsf.png&h=965bec5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3WqJyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3WqJyW.png&h=f9aa8d31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqRRD7h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqRRD7h.png&h=0a906ea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06f5fb47c2b58229101df8b9b92b8821c3c55be2","tid":1382841,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"互相推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovuS</a>"}]}